)" title="Good and evil (disambiguation)">Good and evil (disambiguation)</a>, <a rel="mw:WikiLink" href="./Good_(disambiguation)" title="Good (disambiguation)">Good (disambiguation)</a>, and <a rel="mw:WikiLink" href="./Evil_(disambiguation)" title="Evil (disambiguation)">Evil (disambiguation)</a>.</div>
<div role="note" class="hatnote navigation-not-searchable" about="#mwt2" typeof="mw:Transclusion" data-mw='{"parts":[{"template":{"target":{"wt":"redirect","href":"./Template:Redirect"},"params":{"1":{"wt":"Good and bad"},"2":{"wt":"other uses"},"3":{"wt":"Bad (disambiguation)"}},"i":0}}]}' id="mwAw">"Good and bad" redirects here. For other uses, see <a rel="mw:WikiLink" href="./Bad_(disambiguation)" title="Bad (disambiguation)" class="mw-redirect">Bad (disambiguation)</a>.</div>
