Y">Choksy, J.K. (1989). <i id="mwA4c">Purity and Pollution in Zoroastrianism: Triumph Over Evil</i>. Austin: University of Texas Press. <a rel="mw:WikiLink" href="./International_Standard_Book_Number" title="International Standard Book Number" id="mwA4g">ISBN</a><span typeof="mw:Entity" id="mwA4k"> </span><a rel="mw:WikiLink" href="./Special:BookSources/0292798024" title="Special:BookSources/0292798024" id="mwA4o">0292798024</a>.</cite><span title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=book&amp;rft.btitle=Purity+and+Pollution+in+Zoroastrianism%3A+Triumph+Over+Evil&amp;rft.place=Austin&amp;rft.pub=University+of+Texas+Press&amp;rft.date=1989&amp;rft.isbn=0292798024&amp;rft.aulast=Choksy&amp;rft.aufirst=J.K.&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3AGood+and+evil" class="Z3988" about="#mwt133" id="mwA4s"></span><link rel="mw-deduplicated-inline-style" href="mw-data:TemplateStyles:r879151008" about="#mwt133" typeof="mw:Extension/templatestyles" data-mw='{"name":"templatestyles","attrs":{"src":"Module:Citation/CS1/styles.css"},"body":{"extsrc":""}}' id="mwA4w"/></span></li><li about="#cite_note-34" id="cite_note-34"><a href="./Good_and_evil#cite_ref-34" rel="mw:referencedBy"><span class="mw-linkback-text">↑ </span></a> <span id="mw-reference-text-cite_note-34" class="mw-reference-text"><a rel="mw:WikiLink" href="./Meher_Baba" title="Meher Baba" id="mwA40">Baba, Meher</a>. <i id="mwA44">Discourses.</i> <b id="mwA48">1</b>. 1967. Sufism Reoriented. p. 93. <link rel="mw-deduplicated-inline-style" href="mw-data:TemplateStyles:r879151008" about="#mwt142" typeof="mw:Extension/templatestyles mw:Transclusion" data-mw='{"parts":[{"template":{"target":{"wt":"ISBN","href":"./Template:ISBN"},"params":{"1":{"wt":"1-880619-09-1"}},"i":0}}]}' id="mwA5A"/><a rel="mw:WikiLink" href="./International_Standard_Book_Number" title="International Standard Book Number" about="#mwt142" id="mwA5E">ISBN</a><span typeof="mw:Entity" about="#mwt142" id