<li id="mwBEk"><cite class="citation journal" about="#mwt261" typeof="mw:Transclusion" data-mw='{"parts":[{"template":{"target":{"wt":"Cite journal","href":"./Template:Cite_journal"},"params":{"last":{"wt":"Contestabile"},"first":{"wt":"Bruno"},"title":{"wt":"The Denial of the World from an Impartial View"},"url":{"wt":"http://www.tandfonline.com/eprint/w2bQ5j5xVahrmnPUrjqQ/full"},"journal":{"wt":"Contemporary Buddhism"},"date":{"wt":"2016"}},"i":0}}]}' id="mwBEo">Contestabile, Bruno (2016). <a rel="mw:ExtLink" class="external text" href="http://www.tandfonline.com/eprint/w2bQ5j5xVahrmnPUrjqQ/full">"The Denial of the World from an Impartial View"</a>. <i>Contemporary Buddhism</i>.</cite><span title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=article&amp;rft.jtitle=Contemporary+Buddhism&amp;rft.atitle=The+Denial+of+the+World+from+an+Impartial+View&amp;rft.date=2016&amp;rft.aulast=Contestabile&amp;rft.aufirst=Bruno&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.tandfonline.com%2Feprint%2Fw2bQ5j5xVahrmnPUrjqQ%2Ffull&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3AGood+and+evil" class="Z3988" about="#mwt261"></span><link rel="mw-deduplicated-inline-style" href="mw-data:TemplateStyles:r879151008" about="#mwt261" typeof="mw:Extension/templatestyles" data-mw='{"name":"templatestyles","attrs":{"src":"Module:Citation/CS1/styles.css"},"body":{"extsrc":""}}'/></li></ul>

